OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A former Rwandan army colonel convicted
OL,6, for his role in the massacre of some   
OL,7, 800,000 people in the 1994 genocide has
OL,8, died in Mali, where he was in prison.  
OL,10,FTheoneste Bagosora, 80, was a senior   
OL,11,Ffigure in Rwanda's ministry of defence 
OL,12,Fat the time of the killings.           
OL,14,FA UN-backed criminal tribunal sentenced
OL,15,Fhim to life in prison, but this was    
OL,16,Flater reduced to 35 years.             
OL,18,FHis son Achille told the BBC he died at
OL,19,Fa hospital in Bamako, where he was     
OL,20,Fbeing treated for heart issues.        
